Package: ecap
Type: Package
Title: Excess Certainty Adjusted Probability Estimate
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bradley Rava, Peter Radchenko, and Gareth M. James
Maintainer: Bradley Rava <brava@marshall.usc.edu>
Description: Implements the Excess Certainty Adjusted Probability adjustment procedure as described in the paper "Irrational Exuberance: Correcting Bias in Probability Estimates". The package includes a function that preforms the adjustment and a function that estimates the parameters needed to implement it.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: http://faculty.marshall.usc.edu/gareth-james/Research/Probs.pdf
Depends:
	splines (>= 3.6.0),
	quadprog (>= 1.5.7),
	ggplot2,
	R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
